FOLDER STRUCTURE :

	- "rosick/common" 	: package with common files used by all the tutorials.
	
	- "rosick/mckesson" : package with java porting of McKesson OpenGL tutorials.
	

	
ECLIPSE USAGE :
To test the tutorials, copy or link the "rosick" package into an existing project (in the "src" folder).
If you haven't already done, in the project build path add and configure the lwjgl library.